        revolutionize the future of food automation
      </span><br />by harnessing the power of cutting-edge technology and
      innovative solutions.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div
    id="history"
    class="relative z-10 mt-16 flex flex-shrink-0 justify-center gap-4 max-lg:flex-col"
  >
    <div
      class="our-history flex h-[36px] w-[305px] flex-shrink-0 justify-center font-serif"
    >
      our history
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto flex w-[95%] flex-col lg:mr-6">
      <div class="h-[13px] w-full bg-[#ACC6DD]"></div>
      <div
        class="mx-auto flex h-auto w-full items-center justify-center rounded-br-[120px] bg-[#1A2634] p-16 lg:rounded-br-[292px]"
      >
        <p class="our-history font-serif sm:text-xl">
          <span class="font-bold">Munch Industries</span> started in 2022 as a senior
          design project initiated by a group of passionate engineering students
          from the University of Pennsylvania. Looking to revolutionize the way people
          get their boba, the team set out to create a fully au<span
            class="mr-[3px] italic">tea</span
          >matic boba machine, <a
            href="/orble"
            class="tracking-[2.4px] underline underline-offset-4">Orble</a
          >. Since then, Munch has evolved into a dynamic force in the food
          automation industry. What started as a single machine has grown into a
          series of product launches all built upon the foundation of
          proprietary and patented technologies developed by Munch Industries.
          With a relentless pursuit of excellence and a commitment to
          technological advancement, Munch Industries continues to push
          boundaries and redefine possibilities in the culinary and engineering
          worlds.
        </p>
